OL,3,CFranchisees accuse Vodafone of leaving
OL,4,Cthem in financial ruin
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains
OL,7,Freferences to suicide and mental
OL,8,Fhealth issues
OL,10,F"It's dark, you know, when you're up
OL,11,Fagainst Goliath," Rachael Beedow-
OL,12,FDavison says wistfully.
OL,14,F"I went from hero to zero. I tried to
OL,15,Fplay the game but I was losing money
OL,16,Fall the time."
OL,18,FRachael is reflecting on her career
OL,19,Fwith Vodafone, which began in 2013
OL,20,Fwhen she was recruited to manage the
OL,21,Fcompany's shop in Skegness.
