OL,6,FShe did a good job and was promoted.
OL,7,FIn 2017, Vodafone gave her an
OL,8,FOutstanding Contribution award for the
OL,9,Fperformance of the Lincoln store she
OL,10,Fwas running.
OL,12,FThat same year, she says, the company
OL,13,Fbegan encouraging her to set up her
OL,14,Fown company and go into business as a
OL,15,Ffranchisee.
OL,17,F"It was uncapped commission and you
OL,18,Fhad the backing of the global brand,"
OL,19,Fshe told ITV News. "So I took the
OL,20,Frisk. I was excited."
