OL,6,FHer first year in business was a great
OL,7,Fsuccess. Her company was highly
OL,8,Fprofitable and she was earning twice
OL,9,Fwhat she had taken home as a Vodafone
OL,10,Femployee.
OL,12,FBut during the pandemic, Vodafone
OL,13,Fsuddenly decided to cut the commission
OL,14,Fit paid to its franchise operators.
OL,16,F"My whole world changed overnight,"
OL,17,FRachael said.
