OL,3,CFranchisees accuse Vodafone of leaving
OL,4,Cthem in financial ruin
OL,6,FWithin months, her shops were
OL,7,Fstruggling. For two and a half years -
OL,8,Ffrom early 2022 until July 2024, when
OL,9,FVodafone took back her last shop - her
OL,10,Fbusiness posted monthly losses.
OL,12,FDuring this time, Rachael says
OL,13,FVodafone could see she was in
OL,14,Fdifficulty. She depleted her savings,
OL,15,Fexhausted the insurance money she had
OL,16,Freceived for a Covid claim, took out a
OL,17,FBounce Back Loan and borrowed heavily
OL,18,Ffrom Barclays in order to remain
OL,19,Fsolvent.
