OL,6,FThe pressure of watching her debts
OL,7,Frise and her business fail pushed her
OL,8,Finto despair.
OL,10,F"I just lost it, you know, for a
OL,11,Fminute, I thought it would be better `
OL,12,Fbecause nobody was listening to me `
OL,13,Fthat actually financially my kids
OL,14,Fwould probably be better off if I were
OL,15,Fdead," she told ITV News.
OL,17,F"Which obviously isn't the right thing
OL,18,Fto be thinking at all."
