OL,3,CFranchisees accuse Vodafone of leaving
OL,4,Cthem in financial ruin
OL,6,FIn 2017, Vodafone moved to franchise
OL,7,Fthe 400 shops it owned across the UK,
OL,8,Femploying more than 2,500 staff.
OL,10,FStore managers like Rachael were
OL,11,Fencouraged to start their own
OL,12,Fcompanies and take over the shops `
OL,13,Ftaking responsibility for rent, wages,
OL,14,Foverheads and their own salaries.
OL,16,FIn return, Vodafone agreed to pay
OL,17,Fcommission on every sale made in-
OL,18,Fstore: of contracts, phone upgrades,
OL,19,Fbroadband, insurance and accessories.
