OL,3,CFranchisees accuse Vodafone of leaving
OL,4,Cthem in financial ruin
OL,6,FBut in July 2020 - just as the UK
OL,7,Femerged from the first Covid lockdown
OL,8,F- Vodafone abruptly slashed those
OL,9,Fcommission rates.
OL,11,FSixty-two franchisees claim their
OL,12,Frevenues fell by around 35% as soon as
OL,13,Fthe lower rates were introduced. They
OL,14,Fare now suing Vodafone for "unjustly
OL,15,Fenriching" itself at their expense.
