OL,4,Cthem in financial ruin
OL,6,FMany former franchise operators say
OL,7,Fthey were losing money and had to
OL,8,Fborrow heavily just to stay afloat.
OL,9,FNone of the 62 still operates a
OL,10,FVodafone franchise. All say they've
OL,11,Fbeen left with large debts ` and some
OL,12,Fhave even sold their homes.
OL,14,FDan Attwal ran Vodafone's franchise
OL,15,Fshops in Cannock and Burton.
OL,17,FInitially, he says his business was
OL,18,F"flying" but began losing money
OL,19,Fimmediately after the commission cut.
