OL,6,FVodafone, he says, encouraged him to
OL,7,F"scale" by taking on a larger shop in
OL,8,FDerby. Instead, his losses deepened.
OL,10,FDan fell into rent arrears, took out
OL,11,Fbusiness loans, extended his overdraft
OL,12,Fand borrowed from family. His
OL,13,Ffranchise agreement ended in 2023. He
OL,14,Fstill owes #160,000 to lenders -
OL,15,Fexcluding what he owes Vodafone.
OL,17,F"In one fell swoop, (the commission
OL,18,Fcut) decimated our business," he says.
OL,19,F"I assumed there would be support `
OL,20,Fthat I'd be looked after."
